<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
	xmlns:h="http://java.sun.com/jsf/html"
	xmlns:f="http://java.sun.com/jsf/core"
	xmlns:p="http://primefaces.org/ui"
	xmlns:sec="http://www.springframework.org/security/facelets/tags"
	xmlns:ui="http://java.sun.com/jsf/facelets">
<h:head>
	
	<title><ui:insert name="titulo">Financeiro Web</ui:insert></title>
	
	<h:outputStylesheet library="fonts" name="open_sans.css"/> 
	<h:outputStylesheet library="fonts" name="roboto.css"/>
	
	<h:outputStylesheet library="css" name="bootstrap.min.css"/>
	
	<h:outputStylesheet library="css" name="login.css"/>
	
	<style>
		.center {text-align: center; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: auto; margin-top: auto; }
	</style>
</h:head>
<h:body>
	
	<br />
	
	<div class="container">
		
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-xs-1"></div>
			<div class="col-xs-10 box">
				
				<div class="hero-unit center">
					<h1>Oops! Ocorreu um problema...</h1>
					
					<br />
					
					<h:graphicImage library="imagens2" name="error_icon.png"/>
					
					<!-- <h1><small><font face="Tahoma" color="red">Erro 500</font></small></h1> -->
					
					<br />
					<br />
					<br />
					
					<p>Ocorreu um problema interno, entre em contato com o suporte da Renovar Sistemas para análise técnica da mensagem de erro
					ou volte ao sistema usando o botão abaixo.</p>
					
					<br />
					
					<a href="#{request.contextPath}/restrito/principal.jsf" class="btn btn-large btn-info"><i class="icon-home icon-white"></i> Me leve ao início</a>
					
				</div>
					
				<legend>Detalhes técnicos</legend>
						
				<div class="alert alert-danger">
					<h:outputText escape="false" value="#{ErrorBean.getStackTrace()}" />
					<br/>
				</div>
		
			</div>
		
			<div class="col-xs-1"></div>
		</div>
	</div>
	
	<br />
	
	<h:outputScript library="js" name="bootstrap.min.js" />
	
</h:body>
</html>